        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Back, hip, knee pain and sciatica don’t just hurt - <strong>they wear you down.</strong> They steal your sleep, slow you down, and make everyday tasks feel impossible.</p>",
        "ggpMggARnnc_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-8e88438a-965e-49bd-a32b-a51a7e9ea16a.png",
